content.rendered:
Peacekeeping

Helping Nato, Peacekeeping & World Defence Forces

Seanmag 888 Chlorine Dioxide Water Purification Tablets are available for use for troops for peacekeeping purposes or extensive deployments, whether it be for support troops or contractors.

Due to being low in weight and for having a fast water treatment, soldiers can be issued our product as suitable for treatment for locally collected water.

For short or long deployments, our innovative rain catchment system that is stackable, in-expensive, lightweight, durable, easy to transport, UV resistant, purifies water fast, and can store up to 100L, 255L,500L, 1000L and 2000L of clean water will soon be available.

~ Product coming soon!
